  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_6_3657-3687",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3657-3687",
      "markText": "“日间工夫，觉纷扰则静坐，觉懒看书则且看书，是亦因病而药。”",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3657&rangeEnd=3687",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3657&rangeEnd=3687"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_5_16320-16338",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "16320-16338",
      "markText": "未有知而不行者，知而不行，只是未知。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16320&rangeEnd=16338",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16320&rangeEnd=16338"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_3_9897-9959",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9897-9959",
      "markText": "强调了真知必然要行，表现在两个方面：一是真知具有推动行的内在驱动力，且以行为直接目的；二是“行”是检验“知”是否为真的标准。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9897&rangeEnd=9959",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9897&rangeEnd=9959"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_5_10759-10865",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10759-10865",
      "markText": "爱问：“至善只求诸心，恐于天下事理有不能尽。” 先生曰：“心即理也。天下又有心外之事、心外之理乎①？”",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10759&rangeEnd=10865",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10759&rangeEnd=10865"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_5_18320-18331",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "18320-18331",
      "markText": "知是行之始，行是知之成",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18320&rangeEnd=18331",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18320&rangeEnd=18331"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_7_7920-7970",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7920-7970",
      "markText": "先生又曰：“吾辈用功，只求日减，不求日增。减得一分人欲，便是复得一分天理，何等轻快脱洒，何等简易！”",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7920&rangeEnd=7970",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7920&rangeEnd=7970"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_3_1246-1302",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1246-1302",
      "markText": "王阳明心学形成于明代中叶，作为时代的产物，它直指当时社会物欲横流，道德沦丧，“知而不行”“知行不一”的颓败气息。",
      "totalCount": 100,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1302",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1302"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_6_8970-9021",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8970-9021",
      "markText": "“义理无定在，无穷尽。吾与子言，不可以少有所得，而遂谓止此也。再言之十年、二十年、五十年，未有止也。”",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8970&rangeEnd=9021",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8970&rangeEnd=9021"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_5_4026-4061",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4026-4061",
      "markText": "见其牝牡骊黄而弃其所谓千里者⑥",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4026&rangeEnd=4061",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4026&rangeEnd=4061"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_5_18378-18503",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "18378-18503",
      "markText": "只为世间有一种人，懵懵懂懂的，任意去做，全不解思惟省察，也只是个冥行妄作①，所以必说个知，方才行得是；又有一种人，茫茫荡荡，悬空去思索，全不肯着实躬行，也只是个揣摸影响，所以必说一个行，方才知得真",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18378&rangeEnd=18503",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18378&rangeEnd=18503"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_6_24214-24288",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "24214-24288",
      "markText": "省察是有事时存养①，存养是无事时省察②。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037423&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=24214&rangeEnd=24288",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a2d32fa0813ab751eg0133ab?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=24214&rangeEnd=24288"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037423_5_15411-15468",
